.SYNOPSIS 
    This script starts the HP Array Diagnostic Utility (ADU) and then gives it the command to generate a report, saves it to the root of the current working path in XML format, then parses it to output a list of drives that could be having issues.
.NOTES 
    Additional Notes, eg 
    File Name  : adu.ps1 
    Author     : Edwin Garcia - edwing@gmail.com
    Requires   : PowerShell, PSExec
.LINK 
   <Intranet KB article>
.EXAMPLE 
    PS C:\> .\adu.ps1
